race.comment: FEDERAL BULLET (8) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by a nose (29.50) at this track. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Hard to go past. MY PHARAOH (1) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (29.61) and beaten 0.8 lengths over 520m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. TRIO OF CLOWNS (5) goes very well here starting 18 times for six wins and three minors. Comes off a (29.56) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 520m at this track. Looks one of the chances. TAW GALAXY (4) scored by half a length last time (24.42) in a NG over 440m at Goulburn. Has two wins already from this draw.
